; Coverage for report.cc: group_by option on accounts_report

2024/01/01 Store
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/02/01 Gas Station
    Expenses:Gas     $20.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal --group-by payee Expenses
Gas Station
              $20.00  Expenses:Gas

Store
              $10.00  Expenses:Food
end test
